item.content:encoded:
Are you ready to have a sweet time in downtown Bellefontaine? The Chocolate Walk is back and better than ever! Over 15 local businesses will be offering Ohio-made sweet treats for you to enjoy! With the purchase of your ticket, you’ll receive over half a pound of chocolate and a passport to help you collect it all. Tickets are only $25 and include an empty chocolate box, over 15 SWEET stops to fill that bad boy up, a custom shopping bag, and a passport that includes discounts and promotions as you snack your way through downtown! There's no better weekend to TREAT yourself in downtown Bellefontaine &#x2764;
Your trip starts in The Marketplace – 130 S. Main Street.
Thank you so much to our GENEROUS sponsor: City Sweets &amp; Creamery! Give them a follow at https://www.facebook.com/citysweetsbellefontaine.

Join us this Sunday at The Fun Company in Bellefontaine! We're serving free donuts and juice for kids who create or update their Christmas wish list.
What's a Christmas wish list? It's AWESOME! Do your kids have tons of "I WANT IT" energy?? Channel it all into a wish list that we promise we'll pass along to Santa. We keep the child's wishlist on file at the store and anyone who comes in to shop from it saves 10% and gets free gift wrapping! We keep track of items that are purchased to prevent double-gifting, plus we'll send them a birthday gift in the mail when that comes around &#x1f642;
Can't make it Sunday? Come fill out a wish list any time we're open! We hope to see you soon!

Join us the first Sunday of every month for Donuts &amp; Birthday Wishlists! Does your little one have an May birthday? Now is the PERFECT time to get that wishlist updated - and we'll provide the donuts and juice!
What's a wishlist? It's a list we keep on file for you, allowing your friends &amp; family members to get you the PERFECT gift without risk of double gifting! They save 10% off of anything on your list and get FREE gift wrapping! We'll also send you a special birthday gift in the mail &#x2764;
You can fill out or update a wish list any time we're open, but the first Sunday of every month is going to be just a little sweeter &#x1f642;
